# Patterns to skip when packaging the chart (`helm package`).
# DO NOT add `charts/` or `*.tgz` here — Helm uses .helmignore during chart
# loading too, so excluding charts/ silently makes subchart dependencies
# invisible and you'll get "missing in charts/ directory" errors from
# `helm template` / `helm install` even when the files are right there.

.git/
.gitignore
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
*.pyc

# Local notes
NOTES.md
README.dev.md
